      "span_text": "Another study on malleus allograft ossiculoplasties reported air-bone gap closure of ≤ 20 dB in 81% of cases one year postoperatively, but, in all cases, stapes suprastructure was missing and ossiculoplasty was performed as a secondary procedure, making these outcomes less straightforward to compare [CITATION_3] ."
